    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public Optional<SpecificationLinkType> convert(Map<String,Object> map)
        This method creates an SpecificationLinkType from the values in the provided map. The following keys are expected in the provided map (Taken from EbrimConstants):

        SERVICE_BINDING = "serviceBinding"; SPECIFICATION_OBJECT = "specificationObject"; USAGE_DESCRIPTION = "UsageDescription"; USAGE_PARAMETERS = "UsageParameters";

        This will also try to populate the RegistryObjectType values also looked for in the map.

        Uses: InternationalStringTypeHelper

        Overrides:
        convert in class AbstractRegistryObjectTypeConverter<SpecificationLinkType>
        Parameters:
        map - the Map representation of the SpecificationLinkType to generate, null returns empty Optional
        Returns:
        Optional SpecificationLinkType created from the values in the map
